# Project Overview

This is a Node.js backend for a Pet Startup application. The application provides services for pet management, user authentication, and theme customization.

## Main Entry Points
- [src/server.js](mdc:src/server.js) - Main server entry point
- [package.json](mdc:package.json) - Project dependencies and scripts

## Project Structure
- `src/` - Contains all source code
  - `routes/` - API route definitions
  - `controllers/` - Business logic for routes
  - `models/` - Mongoose models for MongoDB
  - `middleware/` - Express middleware
  - `utils/` - Utility functions
  - `config/` - Configuration files
- `public/` - Static files
- `scripts/` - Utility scripts

## Running the Application
- Development: `npm run dev`
- Production: `npm start`
- Create Admin: `npm run seed:admin`
